{"tid":559757,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"名廚奧利佛旗下餐廳傳欠債29億 將關12分店","createTime":"2018-02-13T12:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T13:30:50.000Z","uid":70985,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f8caec06eedd913814af4ad953732f58f408d2","tid":559757,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T12:44:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2340453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2340453&d=juZNQ8TWd%2FZKTWwpyWEy8oS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=e8242e75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2340453&h=768d62d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2340453</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpxDIqIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpxDIqIY.jpg&h=e0503d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國名廚奧利佛因為常主持電視節目、在世界各地開設餐廳，知名度相當高。不過，他旗下的餐廳最近卻被爆出有高達29億的欠債，計畫會關閉12家分店，台灣分店不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，英國名廚奧利佛（Jamie Oliver）旗下的「Jamie's Italian」義大利餐廳傳出欠債，而且金額已累積高達7150萬英鎊（約29億新台幣）。「Jamie's Italian」為了不讓餐廳王國崩盤，甚至懇求房東能降低房租，奧利佛的債權人也決定減租3成，避免餐廳倒閉。不過為了重組公司，奧利佛25家英國餐廳中，會有12家分店必須關門，預估會造成450人失業。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，奧利佛和他太太的身價高達1.5億英鎊（約60億新台幣），他們之前還曾在社群網站上貼出1000萬英鎊（約4億新台幣）的豪宅照片。他這次會陷入財務困境是因為投資出問題、新餐廳選址不佳，加上經營成本過高。<br />\n<br />\n「Jamie's Italian」目前在台北也有分店，不過台灣代表指出，台北分店現在正常營業中，而且今年還有展店計畫。"},{"pid":"61e51c86cfd4c8b86f9e2af84899bab326622bf8","tid":559757,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T12:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前食過真心唔好食"},{"pid":"3aecaa709ed4c53e772d7252c309f75aaed55c7a","tid":559757,"uid":162424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25f309045663ee1e7b2